// B-tree cursor seek-op codes — sqlite3BtreeMovetoUnpacked direction hints.
// Spec §12.5 — cursor seek.
//
//   GE  — find smallest key >= target
//   LE  — largest key <= target
//   EQ  — exact match (else miss)
//   GT  — strict greater
//   LT  — strict less
// =============================================================================

